                     <interp inst="t18251208-130-person715" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Bertraun - what he has stated is correct.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. The officer asked if it was me or the other young man who took it.</p>
               <p>ANGELIOUS BERTRAUN. I did not.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Three witnesses gave the prisoner a good character - one of whom engaged to take him into his service.</p>
